ActTerritorial Lands Act
SubjectStewart, Scott Douglas ** leasehold interest in an unsurveyed parcel of land **
PrecisOrder authorizing SCOTT DOUGLAS STEWART of the City of Yellowknife, Northwest Territories, an employee of the Government of Canada, Department of Indian Affairs and Northern Development, to acquire a leasehold interest in an unsurveyed parcel of land in the Northwest Territories.
